00:03:41.320 --> 00:03:43.780 align:middle line:84%
So being able to
make sound visible

00:03:43.780 --> 00:03:47.530 align:middle line:84%
is a really wonderful way
of gaining new insights

00:03:47.530 --> 00:03:51.100 align:middle line:90%
